has all the answers</i>

00:09.384 --> 00:11.220
to every question in my life.

00:11.220 --> 00:12.971
I'm going to get him
to tell me them.

00:12.971 --> 00:14.473
Thank you for tonight.

00:14.473 --> 00:18.477
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:18.477 --> 00:20.020
<i>ALISON:
Tyler, no.</i>

00:20.020 --> 00:21.897
<i>SARA:
It needs to stop.</i>

00:21.897 --> 00:23.607
If you having feelings for me,

00:23.607 --> 00:25.484
then you need
to just come out and say it.

00:25.484 --> 00:27.444
<i>What would Clive think
if he knew?</i>

00:27.444 --> 00:29.404
