BERY: We've been in touch.

00:29.404 --> 00:31.490
He sent me something.
I think you should read it.

00:31.490 --> 00:34.743
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:34.743 --> 00:36.578
<i>CLAIRE:
His friend gave him a letter,</i>

00:36.578 --> 00:38.705
which has to be from Edwin.

00:38.705 --> 00:39.790
You got fired,

00:39.790 --> 00:42.125
and you got me
fucking fired, too.

00:48.423 --> 00:49.591
<i>DRAKKON:
Accelerator!</i>

00:49.591 --> 00:51.927
<i>But, yes,
I can increase the power</i>

00:51.927 --> 00:54.846
<i>of any electrical device
to evil proportions!</i>

00:54.846 --> 00:57.099
<i>CARTOON CHARACTER:
Stealing again, Drakkon?</i>

00:57.099 --> 01:00.102
<i>What ever happened
to inventing your own stuff?</i>

01:00.102 --> 01:01.603
<i>DRAKKON:
It's called abstract--</i>

01:01.603 --> 01:03.230
<i>Oh, get on with it.</i>

01:03.230 --> 01:06.358
<i>CARTOON CHARACTER:
How about you get on with it?</i>

01:06.358 --> 01:09.278
<i>DRAKKON: No, it's not the time
to question the nature</i>

01:09.278 --> 01:10.445
<i>of our relationship.</i>

01:10.445 --> 01:11.655
<i>CARTOON CHARACTER:
Okay, fine,</i>

01:11.655 --> 01:13.323
<i>but I am not
doing this for you.</i>

01:13.323 --> 01:15.534
<i>I'm doing this for me.</i>

01:15.534 --> 01:18.245
<i>[suspenseful music plays]</i>

01:18.245 --> 01:21.248
<i>[all screaming and grunting]</i>

01:27.087 --> 01:28.255
<i>Booyah.</i>

01:28.255 --> 01:31.425
<i>[ray gun firing]</i>

01:31.425 --> 01:33.176
<i>Whoa!</i>

01:33.176 --> 01:40.183
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:42.227 --> 01:45.272
<i>[shouts]</i>

01:48.066 --> 01:49.318
BILL:
Man.

01:49.318 --> 01:50.485
No.

01:50.485 --> 01:52.404
That's not acceptable.

01:52.404 --> 01:54.114
I need you to do your jobs.

01:54.114 --> 01:56.241
Every single person
on the island,

01:56.241 --> 01:57.993
