02:24.519 --> 02:26.063
CLAIRE:
Mama.

02:26.063 --> 02:29.066
MIA:
[sniffling]

02:31.109 --> 02:34.112
You need to get dressed
for the funeral.

02:34.112 --> 02:37.157
We should probably take
those out.

02:39.743 --> 02:42.037
CLAIRE: [whimpers]
MIA: I know, sweetie. I know.

02:42.037 --> 02:43.747
But you're so brave.

02:45.957 --> 02:48.835
Almost done with this one.

02:48.835 --> 02:50.921
It really hurts.
MIA: I know, honey.

02:50.921 --> 02:52.839
I--

02:52.839 --> 02:54.841
[sighs]

02:56.676 --> 02:59.763
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

02:59.763 --> 03:06.770
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:09.356 --> 03:11.483
[indistinct chatter]

03:11.483 --> 03:14.486
[distant siren wailing]

03:23.537 --> 03:26.957
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

03:26.957 --> 03:33.922
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:48.895 --> 03:51.773
