04:34.357 --> 04:36.776
SUNITA:
I need you to stop calling me.

04:36.776 --> 04:39.279
CLAIRE:
Look, I feel so terrible.

04:39.279 --> 04:41.364
Okay, yeah, I promise,
I'm gonna make it up to you.

04:41.364 --> 04:42.782
<i>SUNITA:
How?</i>

04:42.782 --> 04:44.910
<i>You gonna pay off
my student loans, my rent?</i>

04:44.910 --> 04:46.453
Are you gonna
get me another job

04:46.453 --> 04:48.371
