from where I live?

04:49.998 --> 04:52.042
Oh, and offers
health insurance?

04:52.042 --> 04:53.460
<i>Didn't think so.</i>

04:53.460 --> 04:55.128
I'm so sorry.
I'm so sorry.

04:55.128 --> 04:58.173
I'm... I'm a fuckup.

04:58.173 --> 04:59.966
I-I got carried away.
I know that, and--

04:59.966 --> 05:02.052
<i>SUNITA: You know what?
Just stop.</i>

05:02.052 --> 05:03.762
I'm done.
This is exactly like last time.

05:03.762 --> 05:05.055
You're not eating.
You're not sleeping.

05:05.055 --> 05:06.348
You're like
a walking time bomb.

05:06.348 --> 05:07.349
And you know what, Em?

05:07.349 --> 05:09.017
I'm sorry
that your sister died,

05:09.017 --> 05:11.228
and I'm sorry that you ran
into the guy who killed her,

05:11.228 --> 05:12.729
but you need
to get some fucking help,

05:12.729 --> 05:14.648
because at this point,
you've become a stalker.

05:14.648 --> 05:16.816
CLAIRE: I know. I'm sorry.
I'm gonna stop so soon.

05:16.816 --> 05:18.568
It's just--I need to know
what's in that letter.

05:18.568 --> 05:19.986
<i>I'm outside his apartment now.</i>

05:19.986 --> 05:21.613
<i>I just need to figure out
how to get inside.</i>

05:21.613 --> 05:24.115
Oh, my God, Emily,
do you fucking hear yourself?

05:24.115 --> 05:26.243
CLAIRE: Sunita, please--
[phone beeps]

05:29.246 --> 05:30.830
Fuck.

05:32.541 --> 05:35.418
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:35.418 --> 05:38.421
GOGO:
[groaning]

05:41.383 --> 05:42.926
PERSON:
Hey.

05:42.926 --> 05:44.094
You dead?

05:44.094 --> 05:46.179
Just checking.

05:46.179 --> 05:49.391
PERSON:
Yeah, I tried to come.

05:49.391 --> 05:52.269
Yeah, I'm saving everything.

05:52.269 --> 05:54.229
Farhad's an asshole.
I hate all these guys.

05:54.229 --> 05:56.231
I got to find a new place.

05:56.231 --> 05:59.234
