07:05.091 --> 07:08.094
[keys jingling]

07:08.094 --> 07:15.060
<i>♪ ♪</i>

07:23.526 --> 07:25.528
[lock clicks]

07:25.528 --> 07:32.535
<i>♪ ♪</i>

07:34.746 --> 07:37.290
[softly]
Fuck, fuck, fuck.

07:37.290 --> 07:39.793
[indistinct chatter]
PAUL: I don't know.

07:39.793 --> 07:42.128
You want a-a breakfast eggroll?
JAMIE: Oh, there you are.

07:42.128 --> 07:44.506
Brett and I got
in a huge fight last night.

07:44.506 --> 07:46.508
He apologized.
I said, "Fine.

07:46.508 --> 07:48.426
As penance, you're gonna
watch the kids all day."

07:48.426 --> 07:49.511
GREG: Yeah.
JAMIE: I'm gonna hang

07:49.511 --> 07:51.554
and gossip with my gays."
[laughter]

07:51.554 --> 07:54.557
EDWIN:
Morning, miss.

07:54.557 --> 07:56.017
TYLER:
Hey, Alison.

08:03.775 --> 08:05.110
What was that about?

08:05.110 --> 08:07.320
Oh, it turns out
Tyler's a closeted douche.

08:07.320 --> 08:09.155
- What's a douche?
